Package com.madrobot.di Description

Data interchange formats(JSON,CSV,XML,plist) Parsing and processing utilities

Included utilities

  • CSV Parser - CSV file reader/writer implementation
  • Plist Parser - .Plist file processor
  • JSON Wizard - Serialization/Deserialization framework for JSON Objects
  • XML Wizard - Serialization/Deserialization framework for XML Objects
